of success (even if the stars aligned correctly?)<br>
<br>
Contrary to popular belief (or at least your beliefs), wasted time is not fun or productive. Saved time is good. If I'm a gimp to you, so be it. I'm comfortable with that if my guild focuses their time correctly and progresses at a solid rate.<br>
<br>
I come here so I save time. I didn't spend the time getting those AA points on Servant of Marr or Frenzied Burnout because information here informed me not to. If people wanted to be asses about it, they could have said what you're saying now &quot;get them yourself and figure out if you want them&quot;.<br>
<br>
And btw:<br>
